Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Forest fires, tornadoes and earthquakes
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjvj9
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 25 Oct 1996
A season of disaster, forest fires, tornadoes, earthquakes and leads to a recollection of a vast storm in 1938 which descended on the Northern Atlantic coast.